description: Outbreak of fever reported from all blocks of East Kameng District.  District RRT investigated the outbreak. Medical camp organised. All cases treated. Out of 10 serum samples collected 1 serum sample was positive for Dengue ( NS1 and IgM ELISA).  IEC on Dengue imparted.
